114
00:10:53,510 --> 00:10:55,150
Is death the only way

115
00:10:56,750 --> 00:10:58,510
to end all this?

116
00:11:09,720 --> 00:11:11,580
You've thought about killing me?

117
00:11:12,240 --> 00:11:13,360
In your mind,

118
00:11:14,790 --> 00:11:17,720
