124
00:11:35,440 --> 00:11:36,360
No matter how badly

125
00:11:36,360 --> 00:11:37,820
you treated me in the past,

126
00:11:38,030 --> 00:11:39,560
I never took it to heart.

127
00:11:39,870 --> 00:11:41,440
But all your kindness,

128
00:11:41,630 --> 00:11:43,120
every little bit,

129
00:11:44,320 --> 00:11:45,910
I cherish it all.

130
00:11:49,120 --> 00:11:51,180
Like this table of food you prepared,

131
00:11:51,270 --> 00:11:53,320
