134
00:12:44,670 --> 00:12:45,240
Here.

135
00:12:49,440 --> 00:12:50,040
Have some.

136
00:12:51,790 --> 00:12:52,390
Eat.

137
00:12:54,000 --> 00:12:54,800
Eat.

138
00:12:54,960 --> 00:12:55,890
It's delicious.

139
00:12:57,120 --> 00:12:58,150
Come on, eat.

140
