152
00:17:08,589 --> 00:17:09,690
Calm down.

153
00:17:12,650 --> 00:17:14,050
Let me introduce myself.

154
00:17:15,260 --> 00:17:16,319
Your husband and I

155
00:17:17,050 --> 00:17:18,200
are twin brothers.

156
00:17:20,099 --> 00:17:21,099
I'm the older one.

157
00:17:21,310 --> 00:17:22,510
He's the younger one.

158
00:17:23,599 --> 00:17:24,660
My name is Su Mufan.

159
00:17:28,500 --> 00:17:30,760
