165
00:17:43,920 --> 00:17:45,720
Why did you suddenly come

166
00:17:46,980 --> 00:17:47,930
to my home today?

167
00:17:49,240 --> 00:17:49,830
Before I tell you

168
00:17:49,830 --> 00:17:50,920
