170
00:17:56,020 --> 00:17:57,150
Did you kill him?

171
00:18:05,200 --> 00:18:05,750
Yes.

172
00:18:07,590 --> 00:18:08,520
How did you do it?

173
00:18:10,030 --> 00:18:10,790
Poison.

174
00:18:11,960 --> 00:18:13,090
Where did you put it?

175
00:18:18,590 --> 00:18:20,720
You don't need to be so guarded with me.

176
00:18:21,240 --> 00:18:22,770
I didn't get along with him.

177
00:18:23,270 --> 00:18:24,440
In a way,

178
00:18:24,460 --> 00:18:25,680
I had a grudge against him.

179
00:18:25,680 --> 00:18:26,700
So I came to see him,

180
00:18:26,700 --> 00:18:28,030
not for a friendly chat.

181
00:18:28,400 --> 00:18:29,660
The reason I tied you up

182
00:18:29,920 --> 00:18:31,060
is so you would calmly

183
00:18:31,060 --> 00:18:32,590
listen to what I have to say.

184
00:18:35,000 --> 00:18:35,920
