196
00:19:42,480 --> 00:19:43,480
might not be you.

197
00:19:45,790 --> 00:19:46,920
Was the wine he drank

198
00:19:47,750 --> 00:19:49,160
brought from outside?

199
00:19:56,640 --> 00:19:57,760
How do you know?

200
00:19:59,470 --> 00:20:01,470
I followed him from Hesheng Street,

201
00:20:05,270 --> 00:20:06,110
where Su Muxin's

202
00:20:06,110 --> 00:20:07,270
lover lives,

203
00:20:07,590 --> 00:20:08,590
all the way here.

204
00:20:09,720 --> 00:20:10,310
When he came back,

205
00:20:10,310 --> 00:20:11,510
he brought a bottle of wine.

206
00:20:11,510 --> 00:20:13,000
So what poisoned Su Muxin

207
00:20:13,590 --> 00:20:14,960
might not be your cup,

208
00:20:15,960 --> 00:20:17,290
but that bottle of wine.

209
00:20:24,920 --> 00:20:26,310
Then let's call the police.

210
00:20:26,310 --> 00:20:26,880
No,

211
00:20:27,000 --> 00:20:28,400
we can't call the police.

212
00:20:28,640 --> 00:20:29,880
You had a motive to kill,

213
00:20:29,880 --> 00:20:31,270
and you actually attempted it.

214
00:20:31,270 --> 00:20:33,270
