216
00:20:34,310 --> 00:20:36,310
who suddenly appeared at the scene.

217
00:20:36,830 --> 00:20:37,610
Now both of us need to save ourselves.

218
00:20:37,610 --> 00:20:38,320
We need to

219
00:20:38,720 --> 00:20:40,160
