for three days at most.

235
00:21:15,880 --> 00:21:16,940
The weather is hot,

236
00:21:17,270 --> 00:21:18,960
so the body will decompose quickly.

237
00:21:18,960 --> 00:21:20,020
Within three days,

238
00:21:20,880 --> 00:21:21,850
