255
00:23:00,830 --> 00:23:01,480
Muxin.

256
00:23:01,920 --> 00:23:03,750
The power will be out at 10 tonight.

257
00:23:03,750 --> 00:23:05,680
Will you come back and stay with me?

258
00:23:05,830 --> 00:23:06,890
What time is it now?

259
00:23:07,480 --> 00:23:08,160
9:30.

260
00:23:08,720 --> 00:23:09,850
